What you need to know:

Chief Justice David Maraga, while opening the modern Isiolo court building on Friday, announced that the judges will be provided with space at the facility to attend to matters pending before the Nyeri court.Mr Maraga, who was accompanied by Judiciary Chief Registrar Anne Amadi and Meru Presiding Judge Alfred Mabeya, also directed courts to ensure cases are finalised in as little time as possible so that justice is not delayed.